INTERSECT
任意分支返回空集，保留返回空集的一个分支，转换为普通stmt
explain basic  select c1 from t1  where 1 = 0 INTERSECT
select c1 from t2 where 1 = 0 INTERSECT
select c1 from t3 where 1 = 0 INTERSECT
select c1 from v4 order by c1;
