RECURSIVE UNION ALL
右支返回空集时，保留左支，转换为普通stmt
explain basic  WITH RECURSIVE my_cte AS
(
select c1 from t1  where 1 = 0 UNION ALL  
select c1 from t2 where 1 = 0 UNION ALL  
select c1 from t3 where 1 = 0 UNION ALL  
select c1 from v4 order by c1
)
select * from my_cte;
Query Plan
=========================================
|ID|OPERATOR                   |NAME    |
-----------------------------------------
|0 |PX COORDINATOR MERGE SORT  |        |
|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR       |:EX10000|
|2 |  └─SORT                   |        |
|3 |    └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR|        |
|4 |      └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |t2      |
=========================================
Outputs & filters:
-------------------------------------
  0 - output([INTERNAL_FUNCTION(t2.c1)]), filter(nil), rowset=16
      sort_keys([t2.c1, ASC])
  1 - output([t2.c1], [INTERNAL_FUNCTION(t2.c1)]), filter(nil), rowset=16
      dop=1
  2 - output([t2.c1]), filter(nil), rowset=16
      sort_keys([t2.c1, ASC]), local merge sort
  3 - output([t2.c1]), filter(nil), rowset=16
      force partition granule
  4 - output([t2.c1]), filter(nil), rowset=16
      access([t2.c1]), partitions(p0sp[0-1], p1sp[0-1], p2sp[0-1])
      is_index_back=false, is_global_index=false, 
      range_key([t2.c1], [t2.c2], [t2.c5]), range(MIN,MIN,MIN ; MAX,MAX,MAX)always true
